Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: dont_research [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaItemPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: excluded [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: included [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: module [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}

Description:

Attribute: research_with [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaItemPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: to_kill [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description:

Attribute: category 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'resource'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'terrain'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'cliff'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'enemy'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: Category name of this prototype.

Attribute: owner 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaEntity', 'LuaEquipment'], 'full_format': False}

Description: The owner of this burner energy source

Attribute: emissions_per_joule 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: The table of emissions of this energy source in `pollution/Joule`, indexed by pollutant type. Multiplying it by energy consumption in `Watt` gives `pollution/second`.

Attribute: fuel_categories 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': True}}

Description: The value in the dictionary is meaningless and exists just to allow for easy lookup.

Attribute: smoke [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'SmokeSource'}

Description: The smoke sources for this burner prototype.

Attribute: signals [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'Signal'}

Description: The circuit network signals last tick. `nil` if there were no signals last tick.

Attribute: signals_last_tick 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'Signal'}

Description: The circuit network signals sent by this combinator last tick.

Attribute: commands 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LocalisedString'}

Description: Lists the custom commands registered by scripts through `LuaCommandProcessor`.

Attribute: game_commands 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LocalisedString'}

Description: Lists the built-in commands of the core game. The [wiki](https://wiki.factorio.com/Console) has an overview of these.

Attribute: commandable_members 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaCommandable'}

Description: Non recursively returns all members of this unit group.

Attribute: members 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntity'}

Description: All entity members of this unit group, recursive (if unit group is member of this unit group, its members will be returned here).

Attribute: sections 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaLogisticSection'}

Description: All logistic sections of this constant combinator.

Attribute: character_additional_mining_categories 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "string"}
Description: When called on a [LuaPlayer](runtime:LuaPlayer), it must be associated with a character (see [LuaPlayer::character](runtime:LuaPlayer::character)).

Attribute: crafting_queue 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'CraftingQueueItem'}

Description: The current crafting queue items.

Attribute: opened [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaEntity', 'LuaItemStack', 'LuaEquipment', 'LuaEquipmentGrid', 'LuaPlayer', 'LuaGuiElement', 'LuaInventory', 'LuaLogisticNetwork', 'defines.gui_type'], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": ["LuaEntity", "LuaItemStack", "LuaEquipment", "LuaEquipmentGrid", "LuaPlayer", "LuaGuiElement", "LuaInventory", "LuaLogisticNetwork", "defines.gui_type"], "full_format": false}

Attribute: consuming 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'game-only'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The consuming type.

Attribute: placed_effect [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerEffectItem'}

Description:

Attribute: trigger_effect [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerEffectItem'}

Description:

Attribute: messages 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'DisplayPanelMessageDefinition'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "DisplayPanelMessageDefinition"}
Description: The full list of configured messages.

Attribute: emissions_per_joule 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: The table of emissions of this energy source in `pollution/Joule`, indexed by pollutant type. Multiplying it by energy consumption in `Watt` gives `pollution/second`.

Attribute: associated_player [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaPlayer', 'PlayerIdentification'], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": ["LuaPlayer", "PlayerIdentification"], "full_format": false}
Description: The player this character is associated with, if any. Set to `nil` to clear.

Attribute: autopilot_destinations 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'MapPosition'}

Description: The queued destination positions of spidertron's autopilot.

Attribute: belt_to_ground_type 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'input'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'output'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: Whether this underground belt goes into or out of the ground.

Attribute: electric_emissions_per_joule [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: The table of emissions of this energy source in `pollution/Joule`, indexed by pollutant type. `nil` if the entity doesn't have an electric energy source. Multiplying values in the returned table by energy consumption in `Watt` gives `pollution/second`.

Attribute: ghost_prototype 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaEntityPrototype', 'LuaTilePrototype'], 'full_format': False}

Description: The prototype of the entity or tile contained in this ghost.

Attribute: infinity_container_filters 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'InfinityInventoryFilter'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "InfinityInventoryFilter"}
Description: The filters for this infinity container.

Attribute: insert_plan 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'BlueprintInsertPlan'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "BlueprintInsertPlan"}
Description: The insert plan for this ghost or item request proxy.

Attribute: inserter_filter_mode [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'whitelist'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'blacklist'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "whitelist"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "blacklist"}], "full_format": false}
Description: The filter mode for this filter inserter. `nil` if this inserter doesn't use filters.

Attribute: inserter_spoil_priority 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'fresh_first'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'spoiled_first'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "fresh_first"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "none"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "spoiled_first"}], "full_format": false}

Attribute: item_requests 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'ItemWithQualityCounts'}

Description: Items this ghost will request when revived or items this item request proxy is requesting.

Attribute: last_user [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaPlayer', 'PlayerIdentification'], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": ["LuaPlayer", "PlayerIdentification"], "full_format": false}
Description: The last player that changed any setting on this entity. This includes building the entity, changing its color, or configuring its circuit network. `nil` if the last user is not part of the save anymore.

Attribute: linked_belt_type 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'input'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'output'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "input"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "output"}], "full_format": false}
Description: Type of linked belt. Changing type will also flip direction so the belt is out of the same side.

Attribute: loader_filter_mode [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'whitelist'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'blacklist'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "none"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "whitelist"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "blacklist"}], "full_format": false}

Attribute: loader_type 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'input'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'output'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "input"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "output"}], "full_format": false}
Description: Whether this loader gets items from or puts item into a container.

Attribute: mining_drill_filter_mode [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'whitelist'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'blacklist'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "whitelist"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "blacklist"}], "full_format": false}
Description: The filter mode for this mining drill. `nil` if this mining drill doesn't have filters.

Attribute: neighbours [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntity'}}, {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntity'}}, 'LuaEntity'], 'full_format': False}

Description: A list of neighbours for certain types of entities. Applies to underground belts, walls, gates, reactors, cliffs, and pipe-connectable entities.

Attribute: removal_plan 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'BlueprintInsertPlan'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "BlueprintInsertPlan"}
Description: The removal plan for this item request proxy.

Attribute: render_player [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['LuaPlayer', 'PlayerIdentification'], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": ["LuaPlayer", "PlayerIdentification"], "full_format": false}
Description: The player that this `simple-entity-with-owner`, `simple-entity-with-force`, or `highlight-box` is visible to. `nil` when this entity is rendered for all players.

Attribute: robot_order_queue 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'WorkerRobotOrder'}

Description: Get the current queue of robot orders.

Attribute: splitter_input_priority 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'left'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'right'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "left"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "none"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "right"}], "full_format": false}
Description: The input priority for this splitter.

Attribute: splitter_output_priority 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'left'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'right'}], 'full_format': False}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "union", "options": [{"complex_type": "literal", "value": "left"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "none"}, {"complex_type": "literal", "value": "right"}], "full_format": false}
Description: The output priority for this splitter.

Attribute: sticker_vehicle_modifiers [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'table', 'parameters': [{'name': 'friction_modifier', 'order': 2, 'description': '', 'type': 'double', 'optional': False}, {'name': 'speed_max', 'order': 1, 'description': '', 'type': 'double', 'optional': False}, {'name': 'speed_modifier', 'order': 0, 'description': '', 'type': 'double', 'optional': False}]}

Description: The vehicle modifiers applied to this entity through the attached stickers.

Attribute: stickers [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntity'}

Description: The sticker entities attached to this entity, if any.

Attribute: units 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntity'}

Description: The units associated with this spawner entity.

Attribute: absorptions_to_join_attack [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'float'}

Description: A table of pollutions amounts that has to be absorbed by the unit's spawner before the unit will leave the spawner and attack the source of the pollution, indexed by the name of each absorbed pollution type.

Attribute: additional_pastable_entities 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description: Entities this entity can be pasted onto in addition to the normal allowed ones.

Attribute: allowed_effects [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'boolean'}

Description: The allowed module effects for this entity, if any.

Attribute: allowed_module_categories [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': True}}

Description: The allowed module categories for this entity, if any.

Attribute: attack_result [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerItem'}

Description: The attack result of this entity, if any.

Attribute: beacon_counter [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'total'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'same_type'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The beacon counter used by effect receiver when deciding which sample to take from beacon profile.

Attribute: boiler_mode [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'heat-fluid-inside'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'output-to-separate-pipe'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The boiler operation mode of this boiler prototype.

Attribute: corpses [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description: Corpses used when this entity is destroyed. It is a dictionary indexed by the corpse's prototype name.

Attribute: created_effect [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerItem'}

Description: The trigger to run when this entity is created, if any.

Attribute: emissions_per_second 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: A table of pollution emissions per second the entity will create, grouped by the name of the pollution type.

Attribute: final_attack_result [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerItem'}

Description: The final attack result for this projectile.

Attribute: fluidbox_prototypes 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaFluidBoxPrototype'}

Description: The fluidbox prototypes for this entity.

Attribute: guns [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LuaItemPrototype'}

Description: A mapping of the gun name to the gun prototype this prototype uses. `nil` if this entity prototype doesn't use guns.

Attribute: harvest_emissions [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: A table of pollutants that this plant will release when it is harvested.

Attribute: indexed_guns [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaItemPrototype'}

Description: A vector of the gun prototypes of this car, spider vehicle, artillery wagon, or turret.

Attribute: instruments [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'ProgrammableSpeakerInstrument'}

Description: The instruments for this programmable speaker.

Attribute: inventory_type [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'normal'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'with_bar'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'with_filters_and_bar'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The inventory type this container or linked container uses.

Attribute: items_to_place_this [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'ItemStackDefinition'}

Description: Items that when placed will produce this entity, if any. Construction bots will choose the first item in the list to build this entity.

Attribute: lab_inputs [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}

Description: The item prototype names that are the inputs of this lab prototype.

Attribute: logistic_mode [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'requester'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'active-provider'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'passive-provider'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'buffer'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'storage'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The logistic mode of this logistic container.

Attribute: loot [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'Loot'}

Description: Loot that will be dropped when this entity is killed, if any.

Attribute: profile [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'double'}

Description: The beacon profile: extra multiplier applied to the effects received from beacon by the effect receiver based on amount of beacons that reach that effect receiver

Attribute: remains_when_mined 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEntityPrototype'}

Description: The remains left behind when this entity is mined.

Attribute: remove_decoratives 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'automatic'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'true'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'false'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: Whether this entity should remove decoratives that collide with it when this entity is built.

Attribute: resistances [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'Resistance'}

Description: List of resistances towards each damage type. It is a dictionary indexed by damage type names (see `data/base/prototypes/damage-type.lua`).

Attribute: result_units [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'UnitSpawnDefinition'}

Description: The result units and spawn points with weight and evolution factor for a biter spawner entity.

Attribute: spawn_cooldown [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'table', 'parameters': [{'name': 'max', 'order': 1, 'description': '', 'type': 'double', 'optional': False}, {'name': 'min', 'order': 0, 'description': '', 'type': 'double', 'optional': False}]}

Description: The spawning cooldown for this enemy spawner prototype.

Attribute: spawn_decoration [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TriggerEffectItem'}

Description:

Attribute: surface_conditions [Optional]
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'SurfaceCondition'}

Description: The surface conditions required to build this entity.

Attribute: shape 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'table', 'parameters': [{'name': 'height', 'order': 1, 'description': '', 'type': 'uint', 'optional': False}, {'name': 'width', 'order': 0, 'description': '', 'type': 'uint', 'optional': False}]}

Description: Shape of this equipment.

Attribute: equipment 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaEquipment'}

Description: All the equipment in this grid.

Attribute: equipment_categories 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}

Description: Equipment category names for the [categories](runtime:LuaEquipmentPrototype::equipment_categories) that may be inserted into this equipment grid. The grid will accept any equipment that has at least one category in this list.

Attribute: equipment_categories 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}

Description: Category names for this equipment. These [categories](runtime:LuaEquipmentGridPrototype::equipment_categories) will be used to determine whether this equipment is allowed in a particular equipment grid.

Attribute: shape 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'table', 'parameters': [{'name': 'height', 'order': 1, 'description': '', 'type': 'uint', 'optional': False}, {'name': 'points', 'order': 2, 'description': 'Only set when the shape is "manual"', 'type': {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'EquipmentPoint'}, 'optional': True}, {'name': 'width', 'order': 0, 'description': '', 'type': 'uint', 'optional': False}]}

Description: Shape of this equipment prototype.

Attribute: input_counts 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint64', 'double'], 'full_format': False}}

Description: List of input counts indexed by prototype name. Represents the data that is shown on the left side of the GUI for the given statistics.

Attribute: output_counts 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint64', 'double'], 'full_format': False}}

Description: List of output counts indexed by prototype name. Represents the data that is shown in the middle of the GUI for electric networks and on the right side for all other statistics types.

Attribute: storage_counts 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint64', 'double'], 'full_format': False}}

Description: List of storage counts indexed by prototype name. Represents the data that is shown on the right side of the GUI for electric networks. For other statistics types these values are currently unused and hidden.

Attribute: pipe_connections 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'PipeConnectionDefinition'}

Description: The pipe connection points.

Attribute: production_type 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': [{'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'input'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'input-output'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'output'}, {'complex_type': 'literal', 'value': 'none'}], 'full_format': False}

Description: The production type.

Attribute: secondary_draw_orders 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'int'}

Description: The secondary draw orders for the 4 possible connection directions.

Attribute: emissions_per_joule 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'double'}

Description: The table of emissions of this energy source in `pollution/Joule`, indexed by pollutant type. Multiplying it by energy consumption in `Watt` gives `pollution/second`.

Attribute: smoke 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'SmokeSource'}

Description: The smoke sources for this prototype, if any.

Attribute: items_launched 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'ItemWithQualityCounts'}

Description: All of the items that have been launched in rockets.

Attribute: logistic_networks 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaLogisticNetwork'}}

Description: List of logistic networks, grouped by surface.

Attribute: players 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaPlayer'}

Description: Players belonging to this force.

Attribute: research_queue 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'TechnologyID'}
Write_type: {"complex_type": "array", "value": "TechnologyID"}
Description: The research queue of this force. The first technology in the array is the currently active one. Reading this attribute gives an array of [LuaTechnology](runtime:LuaTechnology).

Attribute: backer_names 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'LuaCustomTable', 'key': 'uint', 'value': 'string'}

Description: Array of the names of all the backers that supported the game development early on. These are used as names for labs, locomotives, radars, roboports, and train stops.

Attribute: blueprints 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaRecord'}

Description: Records contained in the "game blueprints" tab of the blueprint library.

Attribute: forces 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'LuaCustomTable', 'key': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint', 'string'], 'full_format': False}, 'value': 'LuaForce'}

Description: Get a table of all the forces that currently exist. This sparse table allows you to find forces by indexing it with either their `name` or `index`. Iterating this table with `pairs()` will provide the `name`s as the keys. Iterating with `ipairs()` will not work at all.

Attribute: planets 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'LuaCustomTable', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LuaPlanet'}

Description:

Attribute: players 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'LuaCustomTable', 'key': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint', 'string'], 'full_format': False}, 'value': 'LuaPlayer'}

Description: Get a table of all the players that currently exist. This sparse table allows you to find players by indexing it with either their `name` or `index`. Iterating this table with `pairs()` will provide the `index`es as the keys. Iterating with `ipairs()` will not work at all.

Attribute: surfaces 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'LuaCustomTable', 'key': {'complex_type': 'union', 'options': ['uint', 'string'], 'full_format': False}, 'value': 'LuaSurface'}

Description: Get a table of all the surfaces that currently exist. This sparse table allows you to find surfaces by indexing it with either their `name` or `index`. Iterating this table with `pairs()` will provide the `name`s as the keys. Iterating with `ipairs()` will not work at all.

Attribute: subgroups 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaGroup'}

Description: Subgroups of this group.

Attribute: children 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'dictionary', 'key': 'string', 'value': 'LuaGuiElement'}

Description: The children GUI elements mapped by name <> element.

Attribute: children 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'LuaGuiElement'}

Description: The child-elements of this GUI element.

Attribute: children_names 
Read_type: {'complex_type': 'array', 'value': 'string'}

Description: Names of all the children of this element. These are the identifiers that can be used to access the child as an attribute of this element.

Only top-level elements in [LuaGui::screen](runtime:LuaGui::screen) can be `drag_target`s.
Examples: ["```
-- This creates a frame that contains a dragging handle which can move the frame.
local frame = player.gui.screen.add{type="frame", direction="vertical"}
local dragger = frame.add{type="empty-widget", style="draggable_space"}
dragger.style.size = {128, 24}
dragger.drag_target = frame
```"]

= "hidden"}}
```", "```
-- Lastly, these filters can be combined at will, taking care to specify how they should be combined (either "and" or "or").
--   The following will filter for any entities that are "furnaces" and that are not "hidden".
button.elem_filters = {{filter = "type", type = "furnace"}, {filter = "hidden", invert = true, mode = "and"}}
```"]

